\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n    </span>\n    <figcaption class=\"gatsby-resp-image-figcaption\">6</figcaption>\n  </figure></p>\n<h3 id=\"不可用的选项置灰\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%E4%B8%8D%E5%8F%AF%E7%94%A8%E7%9A%84%E9%80%89%E9%A1%B9%E7%BD%AE%E7%81%B0\" aria-label=\"不可用的选项置灰 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>不可用的选项置灰</h3>\n<p>不能选择的选项不要删除，应保留在视图中并用灰色表示。如果用户将鼠标悬停在变灰的选项上，可以考虑显示一条简短的气泡帮助说明为什么禁用该选项以及如何使其处于活动状态。</p>\n<p><figure class=\"gatsby-resp-image-figure\" style=\"\">\n    <span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 1440px; \"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 30%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,iVBORw0KGgoAAAANSUhEUgAAABQAAAAGCAYAAADDl76dAAAACXBIWXMAAAsTAAALEwEAmpwYAAAAfUlEQVQY05WPiwrCMAxF+/+fqth0Ia/WwpVtjlWcSAOH0HI55CZmx8iy2Nd75Cozkq5k684kYFaoOWp9boj4X2n6/DhDtzvBPNB7R0SgtQazQCk6IzyDIrFdWFvDMWZ1TjjWWXlkBhFD1d91dbbyEdzDpRiIBDnvjNf9Er4AJPjOcWX7l2gAAAAASUVORK5CYII='); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"7\"\n        title=\"7\"\n        src=\"/u-design/static/51a3ff848796d83102021968bd7424ed/07a9c/7-9553252.png\"\n        srcset=\"/u-design/static/51a3ff848796d83102021968bd7424ed/f21e7/7-9553252.png 360w,\n/u-design/static/51a3ff848796d83102021968bd7424ed/37523/7-9553252.png 720w,\n/u-design/static/51a3ff848796d83102021968bd7424ed/07a9c/7-9553252.png 1440w,\n/u-design/static/51a3ff848796d83102021968bd7424ed/e8950/7-9553252.png 2000w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 1440px) 100vw, 1440px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n    </span>\n    <figcaption class=\"gatsby-resp-image-figcaption\">7</figcaption>\n  </figure></p>\n<h3 id=\"通过点击触发下拉框，而不是悬停触发\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%E9%80%9A%E8%BF%87%E7%82%B9%E5%87%BB%E8%A7%A6%E5%8F%91%E4%B8%8B%E6%8B%89%E6%A1%86%EF%BC%8C%E8%80%8C%E4%B8%8D%E6%98%AF%E6%82%AC%E5%81%9C%E8%A7%A6%E5%8F%91\" aria-label=\"通过点击触发下拉框，而不是悬停触发 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>通过点击触发下拉框，而不是悬停触发</h3>\n<p>悬停菜单会迫使用户必须将光标放在菜单内，如果用户光标离开下拉菜单，菜单将被关闭，增加了用户的操作难度。</p>\n<h2 id=\"常见问题\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%E5%B8%B8%E8%A7%81%E9%97%AE%E9%A2%98\" aria-label=\"常见问题 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>常见问题</h2>\n<p>使用下拉菜单是避免用户输入内容的便捷方法，众所周知，打字需要用户付出大量的认知成本，这就是为什么下拉列表在表单设计中很常见的原因。</p>\n<p>但是下拉菜单并不是万能的，使用下拉菜单（尤其是表单中的下拉菜单）时，应平衡表单类型、用户类型等各种其他因素的关系，这需要设计师从众多控件中进行权衡。如：</p>\n<div class=\"u-md-flex-without-bg\">\n   <div class=\"u-md-mr24\">\n      <p><i class=\"u-md-suggested\"></i>当选项很少（5个或更少）时，单选优于下拉菜单</p>\n      <figure class=\"gatsby-resp-image-figure\" style=\"\">\n    <span class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\" style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 1000px; \">\n      <span class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\" style=\"padding-bottom: 36.94444444444444%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,iVBORw0KGgoAAAANSUhEUgAAABQAAAAHCAYAAAAIy204AAAACXBIWXMAAAsTAAALEwEAmpwYAAAAa0lEQVQoz7WR3QrAIAiFe/8XrWhkP7a1K4eNhsEYG7SLgx7QT0WV0kasGNcrdkl/l/deKSVNL0Ksg8+5tpzjE2wAyslaewLABgAoZIwnxJ2cixRCebfhADS+gRjIAGvhBC4fgL+ePO0pM3QA89UaWTTpbYEAAAAASUVORK5CYII='); background-size: cover; display: block;\"></span>\n  <img class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\" alt=\"image alt\" title=\"desc\" src=\"/u-design/static/735a910b2fc2f43f5a6915cea64cc5bd/00d43/8.0.png\" srcset=\"/u-design/static/735a910b2fc2f43f5a6915cea64cc5bd/f21e7/8.0.png 360w,\n/u-design/static/735a910b2fc2f43f5a6915cea64cc5bd/37523/8.0.png 720w,\n/u-design/static/735a910b2fc2f43f5a6915cea64cc5bd/00d43/8.0.png 1000w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1000px) 100vw, 1000px\" style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\" loading=\"lazy\">\n    </span>\n    <figcaption class=\"gatsby-resp-image-figcaption\">desc</figcaption>\n  </figure>\n   </div>\n   <div>\n      <p><i class=\"u-md-not-suggested\"></i>选项较少时，使用Menu交互形式过重</p>\n      <figure class=\"gatsby-resp-image-figure\" style=\"\">\n    <span class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\" style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 1000px; \">\n      <span class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\" style=\"padding-bottom: 36.94444444444444%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"></span>\n  <img class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\" alt=\"image alt\" title=\"desc\" src=\"/u-design/static/cb2299d16cdce46750e7c779e5426689/00d43/8.1.png\" srcset=\"/u-design/static/cb2299d16cdce46750e7c779e5426689/f21e7/8.1.png 360w,\n/u-design/static/cb2299d16cdce46750e7c779e5426689/37523/8.1.png 720w,\n/u-design/static/cb2299d16cdce46750e7c779e5426689/00d43/8.1.png 1000w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1000px) 100vw, 1000px\" style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\" loading=\"lazy\">\n    </span>\n    <figcaption class=\"gatsby-resp-image-figcaption\">desc</figcaption>\n  </figure>\n   </div>\n</div>\n<!--\n\n## 主题\n\n| 内容 | 值           | 默认值  |\n| :--- | :----------- | :------ |\n| icon | icon/nothing | nothing |\n| icon | icon/nothing | nothing |\n\n-->\n<h2 id=\"相关文档\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%E7%9B%B8%E5%85%B3%E6%96%87%E6%A1%A3\" aria-label=\"相关文档 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>相关文档</h2>\n<ol>\n<li><a href=\"/u-design/component/Select/\">Select 选择器</a></li>\n</ol>","headings":[{"value":"简介","depth":2},{"value":"基本构成","depth":2},{"value":"基本样式","depth":2},{"value":"单选菜单","depth":3},{"value":"多选菜单","depth":3},{"value":"多层级菜单","depth":3},{"value":"设计说明","depth":2},{"value":"以可预测的方式对选项进行排序","depth":3},{"value":"描述尽可能简短","depth":3},{"value":"不可用的选项置灰","depth":3},{"value":"通过点击触发下拉框，而不是悬停触发","depth":3},{"value":"常见问题","depth":2},{"value":"相关文档","depth":2}],"fields":{"slug":"/component/list/Menu/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"","description":"为页面和功能提供导航的菜单列表。","order":null}}},"pageContext":{"id":"59e0695a-37c4-56d7-83d6-1556f60cba52","previousPostId":"fbe01b7f-119d-5616-9ad6-183e5502adf1","nextPostId":"3073c598-31ce-5381-bd2b-6e3f0881d224"}},"staticQueryHashes":["3000541721","850322689"]}